[00:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Hi, I\'m Adele. And today, I\'m doing something a lot of you have been asking for. I\'m making a short film starring me with my own voice. Entirely with AI. I\'ll show you the exact workflow I use for making short films. From brainstorming the idea to'

[00:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the final cut. I\'m using nothing but Keith Field. No camera, no crew, no $50,000 production budget. Just Soul Cinema for generating the images, Keith Field audio for the voice, and Cinema'

[00:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Studio to bring everything to life. By the end of this video, you\'re going to have a complete framework you can use to make your own short films. But first, let\'s see what I\'ve made. Happy birthday, my little princess. Want'

[00:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'a cupcake or a parade, maybe? It\'s just a regular day, man. Nothing special. &gt;&gt; Yeah, don\'t sound too excited. Call dispatch, have them sing for you. &gt;&gt; Please don\'t. I\'m trying to keep a low profile. Princess turns 30 year older,'

[01:02] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'that\'s paperwork. Great. Add it to the report. Subject survived another year. So, what\'s the plan today? No alcohol, right? Nah, man.'

[01:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'You know where I celebrate my birthday every year? No. Why should I? Little Central Asian spot on fifth, plastic tables, soup so'

[01:28] [scene:talk]
