VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'new person entirely. Let\'s see what we get. Okay, look at this. For how simple the prompt was, the faces are production ready. The color grain, the skin texture, even the way the light'

[04:58] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'is falling on them. This is the kind of result you normally have to work really hard for to get out of a model. Cuz I guarantee you, if I went to Nano Banana Pro with the same prompt,'

[05:10] [scene:talk]
